{"tid":461560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"給冷漠的香港人","createTime":"2017-11-07T16:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T17:14:21.000Z","uid":74869,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2023471ab9b1e7ef2f916aa83ffb75117a69ce3","tid":461560,"uid":74869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"係現今既香港社會風氣都自我為先 對身邊事物不聞不問<br />\n不論政治定鄰里 最近都成日見到新聞各種自殺風氣 <br />\n加上連登巴打既渲染 令香港呢個悲情城市氣氛更濃<br />\n而最近眼見港鐵 樓梯有女人喊左將近十分鐘  不論職員同路人都視若無睹 而我只盡小小心意 放低一包tempo 告之<br />\n而係岩岩又見到一個年輕女子低頭哭泣 我猶疑了 但同樣地把紙巾遞給他 叫他慢慢用 便走了 但當我走後在想應否回頭 說聲加油 困難總會過去 但又怕被說 唔好做多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   但如果重新選擇 我會說出口 或許就是陌生人的小小關心 少許正能量能令人盡快重回正軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想講我鼻敏感用既紙巾都俾晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c60b56b47abd7389e079fd24b372127834b67da","tid":461560,"uid":121610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"巴打 做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時唔係唔想 係驚人覺得你博咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者人地都係想冷靜下"},{"pid":"731892609a85ffc03e654e94c8ab114e48552554","tid":461560,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"7cff3ffd0546a706015bf7bdf5dfa0c50a275cca","tid":461560,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9715e83d44844caba0db9ec536541381d24d49a7","tid":461560,"uid":74869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時唔係唔想 係驚人覺得你博咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者人地都係想冷靜下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無博咩 唔通拍戲識埋做男女朋友咩 有時一句一個動作<br />\n勝過千言萬語 特別來自素未謀面既陌生人更窩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc1dce469da5141189ca9f5e3006fec04f1d34c","tid":461560,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cb009c784217c538b05e2e8150f8d8487ece3e","tid":461560,"uid":74869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻敏感好撚辛苦</blockquote><br />\n最慘係逐小滲出黎 一定要抺 索唔返上去 嚴重一日幾包tempo 用其他又唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}